german produc price fall 0.3 pct in februari west german produc price fell 0.3 pct in februari from januari and were 4.2 pct below price in februari last year , the feder statist offic said . in januari , produc price rose 0.2 pct from decemb , the first monthli rise sinc octob 1985 , but they were down 4.4 pct from a year earlier . the statist offic said light heat oil produc price fell 22 pct in februari from januari while heavi heat oil price fell 24 pct .